  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM2.2">
<l>tōṭulāmalar maṅkaitōḷiṇai tōyntatuñcuṭar vāḷiyā</l>
<l>nīṭumāmarañ ceṟṟatumnirai mēyttatumivai yēniṉain</l>
<l>tāṭippāṭi yaraṅkavōveṉṟa ḻaikkuntoṇṭa raṭippoṭi</l>
<l>yāṭanāmpeṟiṟ kaṅkainīrkuṭain tāṭumvēṭkaiyeṉ ṉāvatē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Wherefore the desire to bathe diving in the water of the Ganges</l>
<l>if we get to bathe in the dust of the feet of devotees who call [out] saying, ‘O Raṅga!’,</l>
<l>singing and dancing, thinking only of these:</l>
<l rend="indent">[His] embracing the pair of shoulders of the Woman of the lotus who is like a flower,</l>
<l rend="indent">[His] destroying the big trees that grew tall with a glowing arrow [and]</l>
<l rend="indent">[His] grazing herds of cows?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
